                <note rend="inline" type="source">124.84/57: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister Resident in Ethiopia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Engert</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1936-05-04">May 4,
                            1936</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>182. Your 282, May 4, 3 p.m. Can you not communicate with British Legation by
                    radio?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
